description:
&lt;p&gt;Advert for Locum Consultant in Palliative Medicine&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whipps Cross University Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fix term 6-12 months 10 PA&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whipps Cross University Hospital, part of the Barts Health NHS Trust Group is looking to recruit a Full Time Consultant to join our Specialist Palliative Care team based on the Whipps Cross Hospital site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post offers an exciting opportunity to join a growing team and to develop new models of working and services that support palliative care patients attending the hospital and within the local community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This locum post will be based at Whipps Cross University Hospital and work as member of the Margaret Centre specialist palliative care team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time post with the opportunity to develop the Margaret Centre Palliative Care Services at Whipps Cross. Locum post to be developed, encompassing both the inpatient unit and supporting the Community team with advice .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good working relationships exist with all departments within the hospital and with other palliative care teams locally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be full time (10 Professional Activities)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would be happy to consider candidates wanting to work part-time or job share.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If required, applications under Barts Health NHS Trust flexible working policy can be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
